<title>USA: Information Management sets 3-for-2 split.</title>
<headline>Information Management sets 3-for-2 split.</headline>
<dateline>CLEARWATER, Fla. 1997-06-19</dateline>
<text>
<p>Information Management Resources said its board has declared a three-for-two stock split in the form of a stock dividend.</p>
<p>The stock dividend will be payable July 10, record June 26. The total number of shares outstanding after the split will be about 14.8 million, the company said.</p>
